high_descs: Walk up to the door, then turn right and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the ground.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Put the toilet paper roll on the counter in front of the front left corner of the sink.
Walk over to the tub on your right.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the tub.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Put the toilet paper roll on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet paper rolls to the counter.

high_descs: turn right and walk to the toilet paper holder, and look at the floor below it.
Pick up the empty roll of toilet paper from the floor.
Walk over to the left side of the counter.
Put the empty roll in front of the sink.
Walk over to the tub.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper from the back corner of the tub.
Walk back over to the left side of the counter.
Put the toilet paper roll to the left of the sink on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To move a full and empty roll of toilet paper to the sink.

high_descs: walk to face toilet
pick up toilet roll from ground to the left of toilet
walk to face sink
put toilet roll on counter next to sink
walk to face top of bath tub
pick up toilet paper from tub edge
walk to face sink
put toilet paper on counter next to sink
anns.task_desc: put toilet roll and paper on sink counter
